 taking notes.\", \"from\": 3174, \"to\": 3277, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3214, \"end\": 3234, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_England_Patriots\", \"score\": 0.9999999998990461, \"rank\": 8.582494600482613e-11, \"text\": \"New England Patriots\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_England_Patriots\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_England_Patriots\"}, {\"begin\": 3246, \"end\": 3260, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bill_Belichick\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Bill Belichick\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q14128148\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bill_Belichick\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bill_Belichick\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"notes\", \"from\": 3271, \"to\": 3276}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The debate raging across the Olympics athlete village is probably one you have had with your spouse-whether or not to turn on the air-conditioning.\", \"from\": 3279, \"to\": 3426, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The debate\", \"from\": 3279, \"to\": 3289}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics athlete village\", \"from\": 3304, \"to\": 3332}, {\"ngram\": \"your spouse\", \"from\": 3367, \"to\": 3378}, {\"ngram\": \"the air-conditioning\", \"from\": 3405, \"to\": 3425}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Kudos to reporter Henry Bushnell at Yahoo Sports fortaking a deep diveon this topic.\", \"from\": 3427, \"to\": 3511, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3451, \"end\": 3459, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Bushnell\", \"score\": 0.9708260804120792, \"rank\": 0.030050613777662515, \"text\": \"Bushnell\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Bushnell\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Bushnell\"}, {\"begin\": 3463, \"end\": 3475, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yahoo!_Sports\", \"score\": 0.81509619